  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Peacebringer takes the addictive auto-attacking gameplay of Vampire Survivors to the next level by introducing a party system. Build and control a team of heroes, each with their own unique abilities and attack patterns, as they battle against endless waves of corrupted beings. Master positioning and party composition to survive in a world being consumed by a twisted vision of peace.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STRATEGIC PARTY BUILDING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/20197776f99440cf38a46579b25c60ec.poster.avif?t=1743964529\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/20197776f99440cf38a46579b25c60ec.webm?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/20197776f99440cf38a46579b25c60ec.mp4?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 9 distinctive heroes, each with their own abilities and compelling backstories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your ideal party composition as you unlock new characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match abilities like the Ranger's deadly bow skills, the Sorceress's chain lightning, or the Knight's defensive prowess</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MASTER THE CHAOS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/d2faaf600f0ad0ea0b4ed68ced00ba08.poster.avif?t=1743964529\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/d2faaf600f0ad0ea0b4ed68ced00ba08.webm?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/d2faaf600f0ad0ea0b4ed68ced00ba08.mp4?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through waves of corrupted beings in intense, action-packed battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up your heroes by collecting soul gems from fallen enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade abilities or choose powerful boons to enhance your entire party</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase permanent powerups using collected gold to strengthen your heroes</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE A DYING WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/642f0a741bbe48c35ca6db76213f08f6.poster.avif?t=1743964529\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/642f0a741bbe48c35ca6db76213f08f6.webm?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/642f0a741bbe48c35ca6db76213f08f6.mp4?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through 13 unique biomes, from the Whispering Pines to the nightmarish Obsidian Caldera</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle across 39 distinct stages, each with increasing challenges and dangers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new areas as you progress, revealing more of the corrupted landscape</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a diverse array of enemies, from mischievous imps to terrifying dragons</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Peacebringer takes the addictive auto-attacking gameplay of Vampire Survivors to the next level by introducing a party system. Build and control a team of heroes, each with their own unique abilities and attack patterns, as they battle against endless waves of corrupted beings. Master positioning and party composition to survive in a world being consumed by a twisted vision of peace.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STRATEGIC PARTY BUILDING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/20197776f99440cf38a46579b25c60ec.poster.avif?t=1743964529\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/20197776f99440cf38a46579b25c60ec.webm?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/20197776f99440cf38a46579b25c60ec.mp4?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 9 distinctive heroes, each with their own abilities and compelling backstories</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your ideal party composition as you unlock new characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mix and match abilities like the Ranger's deadly bow skills, the Sorceress's chain lightning, or the Knight's defensive prowess</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MASTER THE CHAOS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/d2faaf600f0ad0ea0b4ed68ced00ba08.poster.avif?t=1743964529\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/d2faaf600f0ad0ea0b4ed68ced00ba08.webm?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/d2faaf600f0ad0ea0b4ed68ced00ba08.mp4?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through waves of corrupted beings in intense, action-packed battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up your heroes by collecting soul gems from fallen enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade abilities or choose powerful boons to enhance your entire party</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase permanent powerups using collected gold to strengthen your heroes</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE A DYING WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/642f0a741bbe48c35ca6db76213f08f6.poster.avif?t=1743964529\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/642f0a741bbe48c35ca6db76213f08f6.webm?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3351530/extras/642f0a741bbe48c35ca6db76213f08f6.mp4?t=1743964529\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through 13 unique biomes, from the Whispering Pines to the nightmarish Obsidian Caldera</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle across 39 distinct stages, each with increasing challenges and dangers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new areas as you progress, revealing more of the corrupted landscape</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a diverse array of enemies, from mischievous imps to terrifying dragons</p></li></ul>",
